	<h1 class="title">「票房」《疯狂动物城》留下的不只是票房纪录而已</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/506540/small/506540.jpg?1460267534" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">韩洪刚 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-14 09:40:20 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23820/medium/23820.jpeg?1457918380" alt="" />			
	</div>
